msgstr "使 ``os.urandom()`` 在Linux上阻塞(在系统启动期间)"

#: ../../differences/python_36.rst:52
msgid "`PEP 528 <https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0528/>`_"
msgstr "`PEP 528 <https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0528/>`_"

